<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bordro Yönetim</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #e0eafc 0%, #cfdef3 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .bordro-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2575fc, #6a11cb);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .bordro-card {
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.18);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97);
            border: none;
        }
        .bordro-table th, .bordro-table td {
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .bordro-title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .bordro-card { padding: 0.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="bordro-title">Bordro Yönetim</h1>
        <div class="row mb-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-9">
                <div class="alert alert-info text-center shadow-sm mb-4" style="font-size:1.1rem;">
                    Merhaba, <b><%= user.ad %> <%= user.soyad %></b>! Aşağıda işçilere bordro gönderebilir ve geçmiş gönderimlerinizi görebilirsiniz.
                </div>
                <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card text-center border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="fw-bold text-secondary">Toplam Bordro</div>
                                <div class="fs-3 fw-bold text-primary">36</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card text-center border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="fw-bold text-secondary">Son Gönderim</div>
                                <div class="fs-5 fw-bold text-success">2024 Nisan</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card text-center border-0 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="fw-bold text-secondary">Bekleyen Bordro</div>
                                <div class="fs-5 fw-bold text-warning">2</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="alert alert-warning mb-4 shadow-sm" style="font-size:0.98rem;">
                    <b>Bordro Yükleme Talimatı:</b> Bordro dosyalarını yükleyip ilgili işçiye gönderebilirsiniz. Gönderim sonrası işçi bordrosunu görüntüleyip indirebilir.
                </div>
                <div class="card bordro-card shadow border-0 mb-4">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-4 text-primary">İşçi Bordro Gönderimi</h5>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover align-middle mb-0 bordro-table">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th scope="col">Ad Soyad</th>
                                        <th scope="col">TC No</th>
                                        <th scope="col">Bordro Yükle</th>
                                        <th scope="col">Gönder</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Ali İşçi</td>
                                        <td>34567890123</td>
                                        <td><input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm"></td>
                                        <td><button class="btn btn-sm btn-success"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Gönder</button></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Ayşe Emekçi</td>
                                        <td>45678901234</td>
                                        <td><input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm"></td>
                                        <td><button class="btn btn-sm btn-success"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Gönder</button></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Mehmet Çalışkan</td>
                                        <td>56789012345</td>
                                        <td><input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm"></td>
                                        <td><button class="btn btn-sm btn-success"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Gönder</button></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-info">Bordro Gönderim Geçmişi</h5>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-sm table-striped align-middle mb-0">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th scope="col">Tarih</th>
                                        <th scope="col">İşçi</th>
                                        <th scope="col">Dönem</th>
                                        <th scope="col">Durum</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>01.05.2024</td>
                                        <td>Ali İşçi</td>
                                        <td>2024 Nisan</td>
                                        <td><span class="badge bg-success">Teslim Edildi</span></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>01.04.2024</td>
                                        <td>Ayşe Emekçi</td>
                                        <td>2024 Mart</td>
                                        <td><span class="badge bg-success">Teslim Edildi</span></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>01.03.2024</td>
                                        <td>Mehmet Çalışkan</td>
                                        <td>2024 Şubat</td>
                                        <td><span class="badge bg-danger">Bekliyor</span></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 